  "title": "EVENT SALES AMBASSADOR",
  "description": "<p>Looking for a fun and rewarding career? Join our <strong>vibrant events team</strong> and work with <strong>big brand clients</strong> on exciting campaigns across Singapore!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>💵 <strong>Earn $3,000–$5,000/month</strong> (performance-based)<br>\n🎓 <strong>Full training provided</strong> – no experience required<br>\n🌍 <strong>Overseas trips &amp; team bonding activities</strong><br>\n🚀 <strong>Leadership &amp; growth opportunities</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🏆Your Role:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support and manage events or campaigns</li>\n  <li>Represent clients professionally and deliver great customer experiences</li>\n  <li>Help raise brand awareness and engagement</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>🙌🏼We’re Looking For:</strong><br>\n✅ Positive attitude and willingness to learn<br>\n✅ Strong work ethic and reliability<br>\n✅ Team player who enjoys working with people<br>\n✅ Ready to take on new challenges</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Join a supportive team that values <strong>growth, fun, and success</strong>.</p>\n<h3>👉 <strong>Apply now and kickstart your journey with us!</strong></h3>",
